      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00077"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> A Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168815" type="place">XVIII Sternwartestrasse 71</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00078"/><hi rend="pre-print">Historische Gemälde in der
                  <rs ref="#pmb44816" type="place">Alten Post</rs> zu <rs ref="#pmb40302" type="place">Sterzing</rs>:</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb47422">Zunftfahne</rs>, gemalt von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb44815">Anton Siess</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1794</date></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00077"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb44816">Central-Hotel Alte Post</rs></hi></seg><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">(erbaut 1556)</hi></seg><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">in <rs ref="#pmb40302" type="place">Sterzing a. Br.</rs>
                     (950 m)</hi></seg><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">Besitzer: <rs type="person" ref="#pmb47424"><hi rend="capitals">F. P. Kleewein</hi></rs></hi></seg><dateline rend="right"><date>23 V. 912</date>.</dateline></opener><p>An <rs ref="#pmb428" type="place">Welsberg</rs> vorüberfahrend gedachten wir lieber
               Tage, die wir gern erneuern möchten. Sind übermorgen <rs ref="#pmb182" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Paris</hi></rs>, läng<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens <date>5 VI</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichst Ihr<signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2292"/><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L02070-1"/>Viele herzliche Grüsse
                  <signed>Gerty.</signed><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L02070-1">quer am rechten Rand</note></p></div>
      </body>
